        ## Links Menu Configuration

        ### Dynamic Title
        ```yaml
        title: "%voidchest%'&rs Links Menu - Page (&a&l%currentPage%&r)"
        ```
        - `%voidchest%`: Shows linked void chest name

        ### Link Item Display
        ```yaml
        item:
        customName: true
        lores:
        - "<gradient:gold:yellow><bold>Location:</bold> <white>%location_world%</white>, <aqua>X%location_x%</aqua>..."
        ```
        - Features gradient text formatting ðŸŒˆ
        - Shows world coordinates using:
        - `%location_world%`
        - `%location_x%`
        - `%location_y%`
        - `%location_z%`

        ### Navigation
        Same pattern as Filters menu with:
        - Information paper
        - Page navigation
        - Close button

    </TabItem>

    <TabItem value="upgrades" label="upgrades.yml">

        ## Upgrades Menu Configuration

        ### Menu Structure
        ```yaml
        rows: 6  # 6-row menu (54 slots)
        title: "%voidchest% Upgrades Menu - Page (&a&l%currentPage%&r)"
        ```

        ### Special Slot Positions
        | Slot | Position     | Item      |
        |------|--------------|-----------|
        | 45   | Bottom-left  | Information|
        | 46   |              | Back      |
        | 49   | Center       | Close     |
        | 53   | Bottom-right | Next      |

        **Upgrade Information:**
        ```yaml
        lore:
        - "This menu contains all available upgrades for %voidchest% voidchest."
        ```
        - `%voidchest%` placeholder shows current chest name

    </TabItem>

